---
layout: base.njk
title: 班级作文在线杂志
---
<header class="cover">
  <div class="cover__inner">
    <p class="issue">本地生成 · 老师审定版</p>
    <h1>班级作文在线杂志</h1>
    <p class="cover__summary">收录 {{ publishedArticles.length }} 篇已审查作文，适合手机、电脑阅读，也可生成 A4 打印报纸。</p>
    <div class="cover__actions">
      <a class="button" href="#columns">浏览栏目</a>
      <a class="button button--ghost" href="/print/">打印版</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main id="columns" class="page">
  <nav class="column-nav" aria-label="栏目导航">
    {% for column in columns %}
      {% set count = (publishedArticles | whereColumn(column)).length %}
      {% if count > 0 %}
        <a href="#{{ column }}">{{ column }} <span>{{ count }}</span></a>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </nav>

  {% for column in columns %}
    {% set columnArticles = publishedArticles | whereColumn(column) %}
    {% if columnArticles.length > 0 %}
      <section class="section" id="{{ column }}">
        <div class="section__heading">
          <h2>{{ column }}</h2>
          <p>{{ columnArticles.length }} 篇</p>
        </div>
        <div class="article-grid">
          {% for article in columnArticles %}
            <article class="article-card">
              {% if article.images and article.images.length %}
                <img src="{{ article.images[0] }}" alt="">
              {% endif %}
              <div>
                <p class="article-card__meta">{{ article | displayAuthor }} · {{ article | readingMinutes }} 分钟</p>
                <h3><a href="/articles/{{ article.id }}/">{{ article.title }}</a></h3>
                <p>{{ article.html | striptags | truncate(90) }}</p>
              </div>
            </article>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </section>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
</main>
